 Near the village of{Heathfield}is an{ 
{Industrial Estate}with many factories 
 and warehouses. There is more industry
 in the{Pottery Bridge}area of{Bovey   
{Tracey. Wildlife}is protected within  
 the block with{Devon Nature Trust}    
 areas at{Bradley Ponds}and{Knighton   
{Heath}and the{Devon County Council}run
{Stover Country Park.}Finally the area 
